{
  "stem": "26111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't-- we had a small house at that point that-- we, we didn't-- we didn't have the resources to, to, to-- I mean, we didn't have the staff, and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This friend had both space and somebody to look after her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said goodbye to her there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was convalescing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was getting better, getting stronger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there's no question that she couldn't get out of bed and come to the station, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister was ill with something less grave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- she was-- there was some, some valid reason why she couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had a rather tearful-- both, both farewells were tearful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But-- then my father took me to the station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I have to say, unfortunately, in light of what happened, it was a, a very-- 'we're both men, aren't we?' type of farewell.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And while it was maybe satisfying at that time, in the light of what happened, again, in retrospect, I would rather it had been a more emotional in which we-- scene in which we told each other something of our emotions.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was very little of that that I recall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was full of good advice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was warm.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was-- he was very forthcoming and very positive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but there wasn't-- it wasn't a terribly emotional scene-- openly emotional scene.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The emotions were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were clearly under control.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- in many of the parents, families that I saw there putting children of theirs on the train, there were quite a few that exercised the same kind of self-control.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know what scenes they  had had at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't-- I didn't-- I wasn't observing, I was too busy [LAUGHS] with my own farewells.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
